  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/e95ced92327468b2b0f19a4881a9b4a2.avif?t=1744296699\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras_big/e95ced92327468b2b0f19a4881a9b4a2.avif?t=1744296699 width=800 height=507 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/274fc7aa2d69aef682eeaaecd96cee7f.avif?t=1744296699\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras_big/274fc7aa2d69aef682eeaaecd96cee7f.avif?t=1744296699 width=800 height=300 /></span><i><strong>Honeymancer</strong></i> is a cute RPG with wave-based combat where you play as a <i>Bear Witch</i> who uses honey magic to protect the forest from evil robots and help her fellow neighbours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEEKEEPING & GARDENING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/7335fb753ed607bd1c3c3fe448990f10.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/7335fb753ed607bd1c3c3fe448990f10.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a honeymancer, you need honey to cast spells. Help your bee buddies make honey by planting flowers so that they can collect nectar from them. The more flowers you have, the more honey they make. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a wide variety of flowers that you can choose from, pick the ones you like and fill the forest with flowers!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SAVE THE FOREST</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/6c8b36a8baa5721ebba1ecd612e47ebb.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/6c8b36a8baa5721ebba1ecd612e47ebb.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil robots have invaded the forest you live in, and it is up to you to stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your honey magic to prevent them from destroying trees throughout the forest. The robots come in waves and each wave is tougher than the last. Make sure to use your honey wisely! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a honeymancer, you will unlock and learn different spells that will help you in the fight against the robots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEFRIEND YOUR NEIGHBORS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/122520510d89a86242da77ce7d98a3c8.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/122520510d89a86242da77ce7d98a3c8.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to leave the Bear Witch's comfort zone and befriend the other animals in the forest. Do your best by helping and supporting them through personal quests. By helping them you will unlock new spells, flowers, colors, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being kind and helpful is good for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/c4652b1fb20e8b18bcf923b43953f35a.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/c4652b1fb20e8b18bcf923b43953f35a.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/274fc7aa2d69aef682eeaaecd96cee7f.avif?t=1744296699\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras_big/274fc7aa2d69aef682eeaaecd96cee7f.avif?t=1744296699 width=800 height=300 /></span><i><strong>Honeymancer</strong></i> is a cute RPG with wave-based combat where you play as a <i>Bear Witch</i> who uses honey magic to protect the forest from evil robots and help her fellow neighbours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEEKEEPING & GARDENING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/7335fb753ed607bd1c3c3fe448990f10.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/7335fb753ed607bd1c3c3fe448990f10.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a honeymancer, you need honey to cast spells. Help your bee buddies make honey by planting flowers so that they can collect nectar from them. The more flowers you have, the more honey they make. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a wide variety of flowers that you can choose from, pick the ones you like and fill the forest with flowers!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SAVE THE FOREST</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/6c8b36a8baa5721ebba1ecd612e47ebb.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/6c8b36a8baa5721ebba1ecd612e47ebb.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil robots have invaded the forest you live in, and it is up to you to stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your honey magic to prevent them from destroying trees throughout the forest. The robots come in waves and each wave is tougher than the last. Make sure to use your honey wisely! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a honeymancer, you will unlock and learn different spells that will help you in the fight against the robots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEFRIEND YOUR NEIGHBORS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/122520510d89a86242da77ce7d98a3c8.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/122520510d89a86242da77ce7d98a3c8.webm?t=1744296699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to leave the Bear Witch's comfort zone and befriend the other animals in the forest. Do your best by helping and supporting them through personal quests. By helping them you will unlock new spells, flowers, colors, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being kind and helpful is good for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/c4652b1fb20e8b18bcf923b43953f35a.poster.avif?t=1744296699\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114330/extras/c4652b1fb20e8b18bc